            <title>[THRIFT-264] C# library fails to build in Ubuntu 8.04 and 8.10</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-264</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Ubuntu 8.04 and 8.10 ship with Mono 1.2.6.0 and 1.9.1, respectively and since the current C# library depends on some C# 3.0 features, it requires /langversion:linq&lt;/p&gt;</description>
