                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12664086" author="esteve" created="Thu, 15 Jan 2009 10:54:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Adds /langversion:linq to Makefile.am&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12664602" author="euphoria" created="Fri, 16 Jan 2009 18:33:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This was actually specifically removed in what is currently SVN r665628&lt;br/&gt;
I&apos;m not sure why, but I assume there was a reason? dreiss?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12670117" author="dreiss" created="Tue, 3 Feb 2009 21:15:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I was not able to find a reference for why I removed it.  (I should have put a more detailed message!)  Putting it back.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12670119" author="dreiss" created="Tue, 3 Feb 2009 21:20:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Also included the patch sent to thrift-dev that includes TBufferedTransport in the build since it is kind of related.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12670122" author="euphoria" created="Tue, 3 Feb 2009 21:28:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;So, I actually have a patch for this that makes it work without the requires... I didn&apos;t realize this was going to get checked in.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12670133" author="euphoria" created="Tue, 3 Feb 2009 22:02:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The extra fix tacked on to this check-in included part of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-258&quot; title=&quot;TBufferedTransport.cs missing in lib/csharp/Makefile.am&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;THRIFT-258&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;THRIFT-258&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, but not all &amp;#8211;  could you apply the rest of the patch there?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12670142" author="dreiss" created="Tue, 3 Feb 2009 22:14:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sorry about that.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12670147" author="euphoria" created="Tue, 3 Feb 2009 22:17:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve attached a patch against the new trunk on &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-258&quot; title=&quot;TBufferedTransport.cs missing in lib/csharp/Makefile.am&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;THRIFT-258&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;THRIFT-258&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; if it makes it any easier.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Edit: No worries, of course.  Progress is always welcome.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
